					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The response looks confident, but it's typically wrong. We can nudge the LLM by providing explanations in the system instructions:"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [
