							"code" : "c := GtLChat new\n\t\tmarkdownResponse;\n\t\tgtPageExplanation: 'Rewriting Pharo code by example';\n\t\taddResponseFormatForMagrite: GtLRewriteRule named: 'RewriteRule';\n\t\tsendMarkdown: 'Provide the rewrite rule for removing all `self halt` statements from methods.'"
